        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Moniligaster bahli Narayanan & Julka, sp. nov. A. Ventral view. B. Prostate of left hand side, dorsal view. C. Prostatic capsule of left hand side, dorsal view. D. Spermatheca of right hand side, dorsal view. E. Spermathecal atrial glands, ventral view. Abbreviations. C.Atr.D.—Common atrial duct; M.H.L.—Mass of hairpin loops; Pr.C.—Prostatic capsule; Pr.— Prostate; Pr.D.—Prostatic duct; Sp.A.—Spermathecal ampulla; Sp.Atr.G.—Spermathecal atrial gland; Sp.D.—Spermathecal duct; S.M.A.—Secondary male aperture; Sp.P.—Spermathecal pore; T.S.—Testis sac; Vd—Vas deferens." ;
